OL,5,EDEAR STORM FLY BABY                    
OL,7,BGetting a response has put a spring in 
OL,8,Bmy step and daydreaming is what I do   
OL,9,Bbest.  Why live in the world when you  
OL,10,Bcan live in your head?                 
OL,12,B'Ziners, join usBin the battle against 
OL,13,Bthis conformist state. Don't follow    
OL,14,Btrends, they will have changed by      
OL,15,Btomorrow. Just follow your self.G      
OL,16,G                                       
OL,18,EAlcopop Boy                            
