OL,5,EINSOMNIA                               
OL,7,BLying awake, it's sleep I fear. My mind
OL,8,Bcan't rest while my brain is in gear.  
OL,9,BHeadphone pipes tune to my muted ears. 
OL,10,BA concert of noise only I am s'posed to
OL,11,Bhear.                                  
OL,13,BThe curtains open, the sky is clear.   
OL,14,BI wait all night for the sun to appear.
OL,15,BThe night bores on, my head feels queer
OL,16,BFrom tired eyes there comes a tear.    
OL,18,EEidolon (Machinehead's bro')           
